#: ../../../intro.rst:8
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介紹"

#: ../../../intro.rst:10
msgid ""
"This is the documentation for discord.py, a library for Python to aid in "
"creating applications that utilise the Discord API."
msgstr ""
"這是 discord.py 的文件，discord.py 是一個 Python 程式庫，用於協助建立使用 "
"Discord API 的應用程式。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:14
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "必要條件"

#: ../../../intro.rst:16
msgid ""
"discord.py works with Python 3.8 or higher. Support for earlier versions of "
"Python is not provided. Python 2.7 or lower is not supported. Python 3.7 or "
"lower is not supported."
msgstr ""
"discord.py 支援 Python 3.8 或更高版本。不提供對較舊 Python 版本的支援。不支"
"援 Python 2.7 或更低版本。不支援 Python 3.7 或更低版本。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:23
msgid "Installing"
msgstr "安裝"

#: ../../../intro.rst:25
msgid "You can get the library directly from PyPI: ::"
msgstr "您可以直接從 PyPI 取得此程式庫： ::"

#: ../../../intro.rst:27
msgid "python3 -m pip install -U discord.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:29
msgid "If you are using Windows, then the following should be used instead: ::"
msgstr "如果您使用的是 Windows，則應改用以下指令： ::"

#: ../../../intro.rst:31
msgid "py -3 -m pip install -U discord.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:34
msgid ""
"To get voice support, you should use ``discord.py[voice]`` instead of "
"``discord.py``, e.g. ::"
msgstr ""
"若要取得語音支援，您應使用 ``discord.py[voice]`` 而非 ``discord.py``，例"
"如： ::"

#: ../../../intro.rst:36
msgid "python3 -m pip install -U discord.py[voice]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:38
msgid ""
"On Linux environments, installing voice requires getting the following "
"dependencies:"
msgstr "在 Linux 環境中，安裝語音支援需要取得以下依賴："

#: ../../../intro.rst:40
msgid "`libffi <https://github.com/libffi/libffi>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:41
msgid "`libnacl <https://github.com/saltstack/libnacl>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:42
msgid "`python3-dev <https://packages.debian.org/python3-dev>`_"
msgstr "python3-dev <https://packages.debian.org/python3-dev>`_"

#: ../../../intro.rst:44
msgid ""
"For a Debian-based system, the following command will get these dependencies:"
msgstr "對於基於 Debian 的系統，以下命令可以取得這些依賴："

#: ../../../intro.rst:46
msgid "$ apt install libffi-dev libnacl-dev python3-dev"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:50
msgid "Remember to check your permissions!"
msgstr "請記得檢查您的權限！"

#: ../../../intro.rst:53
msgid "Virtual Environments"
msgstr "虛擬環境"

#: ../../../intro.rst:55
msgid ""
"Sometimes you want to keep libraries from polluting system installs or use a "
"different version of libraries than the ones installed on the system. You "
"might also not have permissions to install libraries system-wide. For this "
"purpose, the standard library as of Python 3.3 comes with a concept called "
"\"Virtual Environment\"s to help maintain these separate versions."
msgstr ""
"有時您可能希望避免程式庫污染系統安裝，或需要使用與系統上已安裝版本不同的程式"
"庫。您也可能沒有全系統安裝程式庫的權限。為此，Python 3.3 起標準庫提供了一個稱"
"為「虛擬環境」的概念，來協助維護這些獨立的版本。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:60
msgid "A more in-depth tutorial is found on :doc:`py:tutorial/venv`."
msgstr "更深入的教學請參考 :doc:`py:tutorial/venv`。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:62
msgid "However, for the quick and dirty:"
msgstr "不過，以下是快速上手的方法："

#: ../../../intro.rst:64
msgid "Go to your project's working directory:"
msgstr "前往您的專案的工作目錄："

#: ../../../intro.rst:66
msgid ""
"$ cd your-bot-source\n"
"$ python3 -m venv bot-env"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:71
msgid "Activate the virtual environment:"
msgstr "激活虛擬環境："

#: ../../../intro.rst:73
msgid "$ source bot-env/bin/activate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:77
msgid "On Windows you activate it with:"
msgstr "在 Windows 上，您可以這樣激活虛擬環境："

#: ../../../intro.rst:79
msgid "$ bot-env\\Scripts\\activate.bat"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:83
msgid "Use pip like usual:"
msgstr "像平常一樣使用 pip："

#: ../../../intro.rst:85
msgid "$ pip install -U discord.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro.rst:89
msgid "Congratulations. You now have a virtual environment all set up."
msgstr "恭喜！您現在已經設定好虛擬環境了。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:93
msgid ""
"Scripts executed with ``py -3`` will ignore any currently active virtual "
"environment, as the ``-3`` specifies a global scope."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``py -3`` 執行的腳本會忽略當前已激活的虛擬環境，因為 ``-3`` 指定了全域範"
"圍。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:97
msgid "Basic Concepts"
msgstr "基礎概念"

#: ../../../intro.rst:99
msgid ""
"discord.py revolves around the concept of :ref:`events <discord-api-"
"events>`. An event is something you listen to and then respond to. For "
"example, when a message happens, you will receive an event about it that you "
"can respond to."
msgstr ""
"discord.py 的核心概念是 :ref:`事件 <discord-api-events>`。事件是您監聽並回應"
"的事物。例如，當有新訊息時，您會收到一個關於該訊息的事件，然後您可以對其做出"
"回應。"

#: ../../../intro.rst:103
msgid "A quick example to showcase how events work:"
msgstr "以下是一個快速展示事件運作方式的範例："

#: ../../../intro.rst:105
msgid ""
"# This example requires the 'message_content' intent.\n"
"\n"
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"class MyClient(discord.Client):\n"
"    async def on_ready(self):\n"
"        print(f'Logged on as {self.user}!')\n"
"\n"
"    async def on_message(self, message):\n"
"        print(f'Message from {message.author}: {message.content}')\n"
"\n"
"intents = discord.Intents.default()\n"
"intents.message_content = True\n"
"\n"
"client = MyClient(intents=intents)\n"
"client.run('my token goes here')"
msgstr ""
"# 此範例需要 'message_content' intent。\n"
"\n"
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"class MyClient(discord.Client):\n"
"    async def on_ready(self):\n"
"        print(f'Logged on as {self.user}!')\n"
"\n"
"    async def on_message(self, message):\n"
"        print(f'Message from {message.author}: {message.content}')\n"
"\n"
"intents = discord.Intents.default()\n"
"intents.message_content = True\n"
"\n"
"client = MyClient(intents=intents)\n"
"client.run('my token goes here')"
